0x60FB60FE.name: GET_TIMECYCLE_MODIFIER_VAR_COUNT

examples.code:
local varCount = GetTimecycleModifierVarCount("underwater")

if varCount ~= 0 then
  for index = 0, varCount - 1 do
    local varName = GetTimecycleModifierVarNameByIndex(index)

    print(string.format("[%d] %s", index, varName))
  end
end

0x60FB60FE.resultsDescription: The amount of variables used on a specified timecycle modifier.
